title: The Zeitathlon 2/15: Alec Baldwin, NYT, Remington, Coachella, Sarah Palin, Elon Musk, Rescue Rangers
itunes:title: The Zeitathlon 2/15: Alec Baldwin, NYT, Remington, Coachella, Sarah Palin, Elon Musk, Rescue Rangers
description:
In this edition of The Zeitathlon, Jack and Miles discuss Alec Baldwin getting sued by the family of Halyna Hutchins, the NYT's unsympathetic pandemic housing market article, Remington and Prince Andrew having a bad day in court, Coachella time-travelling back to 2019, Sarah Palin vs. NYT, Elon Musk pledging to donate $6 billion if UN can detail ending world hunger, and the new 'Rescue Rangers' trailer
